1
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,120
My father

2
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,680
suffered a heart attack on the spot from anger

3
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,600
and passed away suddenly.

4
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,880
Our Duan Family

5
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,080
has been in decline ever since.

6
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,880
But what about you?

7
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:30,840
Even now,

8
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:34,040
you haven't offered a single word of explanation.

9
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,040
Since that's the case,

10
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,720
from now on,

11
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,280
we will go our separate ways completely.

12
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,160
Forget about me from now on.

13
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,720
Qingqing.

14
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,440
Inspector.

15
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:56,760
Don't you have your reasons?

16
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,320
You should just explain what happened a year ago

17
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,360
to Qingqing.

18
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,120
Inspector,

19
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,000
I don't want to see you two

20
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,920
end up like this.

21
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:11,120
Qingqing,

22
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,400
actually, a year ago,

23
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,400
the reason I left the wedding

24
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,000
was because my mother, Su Yao,

25
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,000
died that day.

26
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,400
What did you say?

27
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,640
Your mother...

28
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,200
Our great Inspector

29
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,120
is finally going to be with Qingqing

30
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,920
and live a happy life everyone envies.

31
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,560
You should hurry up too.

32
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,400
Okay.

33
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,560
Look at the time,

34
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,000
why hasn't my mother

35
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:58,920
arrived at the church yet?

36
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,280
We've already sent someone to pick her up.

37
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,280
Looking at the time,

38
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,120
she should be here soon.

39
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,080
Something happened to Madam!

40
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,840
Where are you going?

41
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:23,840
Qingqing,

42
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,720
I'll be right back!

43
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,200
Inspector!

44
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,560
I was completely in shock at the time,

45
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,520
so I rushed out of the church without a second thought.

46
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,560
It turned out,

47
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,360
the killer

48
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,400
took advantage of everyone being at the wedding

49
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,280
to sneak into the house

50
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,600
and brutally murder my mother.

51
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,440
But my father

52
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,320
immediately

53
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,680
blocked the news of my mother's death.

54
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,840
Mom!

55
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,520
Mom!

56
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,200
Look at me!

57
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,120
Mom!

58
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:32,760
You mean

59
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,760
your mother's cause of death

60
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,880
is exactly the same as your father's?

61
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,440
No wonder

62
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:48,280
you said the killer is the same person.

63
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,080
Qingqing,

64
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,840
I know I've wronged you.

65
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,320
But all of this

66
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:56,080
haunts me like a nightmare.

67
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,320
Then why did you keep it from me?

68
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,200
Because I didn't want to drag you into this.

69
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,120
I was afraid it would bring you harm.

70
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,400
So,

71
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,120
I didn't dare...

72
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,840
I didn't dare tell you.

73
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,440
Then what did you find out back then?

74
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,000
I found absolutely nothing.

75
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:30,080
I found absolutely nothing.

76
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:32,960
How is that possible?

77
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,320
I remember on the day of our wedding,

78
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,640
the Marshal's Residence

79
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,880
conducted a citywide manhunt.

80
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,080
How could they not find the killer?

81
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,440
It was exactly because of

82
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,560
that manhunt.

83
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:49,880
Father.

84
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,440
Don't you know to knock before entering?

85
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,080
Who taught you to be so ill-mannered?

86
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,720
You sending people out like this

87
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,880
to make mass arrests in the city,

88
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,280
don't you know

89
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,080
this will seriously interfere with my investigation?

90
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,080
You do your investigation,

91
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,320
and I'll do my search.

92
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,560
How does it interfere with you?

93
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:07,760
Doing things your way

94
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,120
is just alerting the enemy.

95
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,720
Your large-scale manhunt

96
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,440
will only make the killer who murdered my mom

97
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,200
more vigilant,

98
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:14,960
and then go into hiding.

99
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,120
How am I supposed to investigate then?

100
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,960
I know what I'm doing.

101
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,760
It's not your place to be here

102
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,520
dictating what I should do.

103
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,120
You are acting blindly.

104
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,000
Without knowing anything about the killer,

105
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,200
it will only make things worse

106
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,000
and lose the chance to catch them.

107
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,640
Let me tell you,

108
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,560
I am Jiangyu City's

109
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,520
highest commander.

110
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,840
It's not your place to teach me what to do.

111
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,520
You'll only give the killer

112
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,280
an opportunity to escape.

113
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,520
I advise you to listen to my opinion

114
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,760
and not act so arbitrarily.

115
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,560
You say I act arbitrarily?

116
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:44,960
You rebellious son!

117
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,960
Get out of here!

118
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,760
Get out of here!

119
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,560
Get out!

120
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,960
Just because of his arbitrary actions,

121
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,080
I missed

122
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,560
the best opportunity to catch the killer.

123
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,640
I never expected

124
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,320
that this time it would be my father.

125
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,120
Now the killer has appeared again.

126
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,120
I'll help you look for them.

127
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,760
We will definitely find the killer.

128
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,440
Inspector,

129
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,760
then where do we

130
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,320
start investigating now?

131
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,080
Be careful.

132
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,520
Inspector.

133
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,520
Since this killer

134
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,880
is someone both my parents knew,

135
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:52,720
then we should

136
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,880
carefully sort through the clues,

137
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,000
and start with the people

138
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,880
around my mother.

139
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,320
Who did this?

140
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,240
Changsheng.

141
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,720
Why him?

142
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,960
Isn't this Marshal Huang's nephew,

143
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,720
the youngest in our Jiangyu City,

144
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,240
President of the Chamber of Commerce,

145
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,240
Huang Changsheng?

146
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,840
What on earth is happening to the Huang family?

147
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,200
First it was Marshal Huang,

148
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,320
and now,

149
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,560
even President Huang...

150
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,840
They probably provoked

151
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,160
something unclean.

152
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,440
What nonsense are you all talking about?

153
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,840
All of you, shut up!

154
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,080
The victim is bleeding from the seven orifices.

155
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,360
Preliminary assessment

156
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,720
suggests death by asphyxiation.

157
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,320
Asphyxiation again?

158
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:42,080
The cause of death is too bizarre.

159
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,960
I need to conduct a further examination

160
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,320
before I can make a final determination.

161
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,440
We

162
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,240
will definitely find the killer.
